    <h1>Helpful Websites for Dungeons & Dragons</h1>
    <div>
        <h2><a href="https://roll20.net/">Roll20</a></h2>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Virtual Tabletop (VTT) platform</p>
        <p><strong>Why It's Helpful:</strong> Roll20 allows you to play D&D online with friends, offering maps, dice rollers, character sheets, and automated mechanics for D&D 5E and other systems.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2><a href="https://www.dndbeyond.com/">D&D Beyond</a></h2>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Official digital toolset for D&D</p>
        <p><strong>Why It's Helpful:</strong> D&D Beyond provides digital rulebooks, character sheets, and campaign management tools, making it easy to play and organize your games.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2><a href="https://donjon.bin.sh/">Donjon</a></h2>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Random generators for D&D</p>
        <p><strong>Why It's Helpful:</strong> Donjon is a quick and easy resource for generating dungeons, NPCs, encounters, and treasure, perfect for spontaneous game prep.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2><a href="https://www.dmsguild.com/">The Dungeon Master's Guild</a></h2>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Marketplace for D&D content</p>
        <p><strong>Why It's Helpful:</strong> Find fan-made modules, supplements, and adventures for D&D, and share or sell your own creations.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2><a href="https://kobold.club/">Kobold Fight Club</a></h2>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Encounter generator for DMs</p>
        <p><strong>Why It's Helpful:</strong> Kobold Fight Club helps DMs create balanced combat encounters based on the party's level and number, making it easier to run challenging battles.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
        <h2><a href="https://foundryvtt.com/">Foundry VTT</a></h2>
        <p><strong>Purpose:</strong> Virtual Tabletop (VTT) platform</p>
        <p><strong>Why It's Helpful:</strong> Foundry VTT is a customizable virtual tabletop with dynamic lighting, interactive maps, and automated gameplay features.</p>
    </div>
